03:55.860 --> 03:57.111
It isn't us.

03:57.820 --> 04:00.740
Which is exactly why we're going to do it.

04:01.282 --> 04:03.201
[theme music playing]

04:08.706 --> 04:10.583
Hey, Dante. You got a sec?

04:10.667 --> 04:12.168
Hey, yeah. What's up?

04:12.252 --> 04:13.086
Well...

04:14.379 --> 04:17.340
