41:26.817 --> 41:28.068
[Cary screams]

42:47.439 --> 42:48.482
Are you okay?

43:19.054 --> 43:20.764
[moaning]

43:35.279 --> 43:36.905
Holy fucking shit.

43:39.241 --> 43:41.243
I think that was the best sex
we've ever had.

43:41.327 --> 43:43.579
[Joe] Yes, it was.

43:44.330 --> 43:48.000
The spark our marriage needed
doesn't come from swinging.

43:49.501 --> 43:51.754
Our love language is violence.

44:07.269 --> 44:08.103
[Joe] Shit.

44:11.273 --> 44:14.902
-Hey.
-What happened to the car?

44:16.278 --> 44:20.240
Love spilled fruit sauce.
So I'm just getting it before it sets in.

44:20.324 --> 44:21.617
At 5 a.m.?

44:22.993 --> 44:24.328
Couldn't sleep.

44:24.411 --> 44:26.413
Doesn't look like he's gotten much either.

44:26.497 --> 44:27.498
You okay?

44:32.586 --> 44:33.796
What was that last night?

44:33.879 --> 44:37.257
Last night? Oh, we were--
I mean, were we that loud?

44:38.133 --> 44:41.637
We had a kid with a sitter,
had a little fun.

44:41.720 --> 44:44.264
With the Conrads? I saw their car.

44:45.391 --> 44:48.227
Yeah, they were here for a second. Yeah.

44:48.310 --> 44:49.520
Oh.

44:50.646 --> 44:52.523
I thought I heard someone scream.

44:55.818 --> 45:00.823
It was drunken shenanigans.
It was harmless, really. I'm embarrassed.

45:00.906 --> 45:02.908
Stupid fun, really.

45:02.991 --> 45:06.328
Yeah, you and your wife, Love.
Just having fun.

45:08.956 --> 45:13.127
Yeah, again,
I apologize if it disturbed you.

45:13.210 --> 45:16.130
We were saying we should have you over
for dinner sometime soon.

45:16.213 --> 45:18.048
Yeah, real busy with work. But sometime.

45:19.842 --> 45:20.759
Sometime.

45:51.749 --> 45:53.500
I put my best friend...

45:55.043 --> 45:56.628
in a cage.

45:58.881 --> 46:00.340
Oh, my God.

46:02.551 --> 46:05.554
I am so grateful for you.

46:07.014 --> 46:10.225
I don't know anybody else
who would understand.

46:11.226 --> 46:13.437
I don't know what I'd do without you.

46:21.653 --> 46:22.571
Okay.

46:23.322 --> 46:24.907
I'm gonna make breakfast

46:24.990 --> 46:29.411
and then I can contact Henry's sitter
to see if they'll take him longer.

46:29.495 --> 46:31.163
We can just clean up.

46:31.246 --> 46:33.582
We'll go over there.
We'll "good cop, bad cop" them.

46:33.665 --> 46:36.543
[Joe] She's too good at this now.
This should not be routine.

46:36.627 --> 46:38.587
We will get through this, okay?

46:38.670 --> 46:43.133
I don't want to, I want you--
Shit. Your custody hearing.

46:44.134 --> 46:45.093
Joe?

46:45.177 --> 46:49.598
I forgot, I promised to fill in for Dante.
He's got a thing and I have to--

46:49.681 --> 46:53.310
I'll be fast, meet you soon as I'm done.
Don't do anything until I get there.

46:55.938 --> 46:58.941
-You are, as ever, an inspiration.
-Thank you.

47:00.192 --> 47:01.777
Well, that happened.

47:01.860 --> 47:03.862
-You killed it.
-You were so great.

47:03.946 --> 47:06.156
-Yeah?
-Yeah. Flawless, unimpeachable.

47:06.240 --> 47:08.367
Dare I say, unironically,
mother of the year.

47:08.450 --> 47:11.161
I'm so glad you were here. Both of you.

47:12.746 --> 47:13.831
Thank you.

47:20.337 --> 47:21.797
[inaudible dialogue]

47:23.924 --> 47:25.259
What was that?

47:26.218 --> 47:28.512
Are Ryan and the judge friends?

47:32.224 --> 47:35.269
You were right. The system is rigged.

47:35.352 --> 47:37.604
Come on, Dante. We're gonna go.

47:39.189 --> 47:42.985
And as long as he's in the picture,
you are always going to lose.

47:50.701 --> 47:53.078
Hey. You good?

47:54.454 --> 47:56.456
Yeah, I'm okay. What about--?

47:56.540 --> 47:59.668
Oh, they're-- They're just waking up.

48:05.382 --> 48:06.216
Hey.

48:08.051 --> 48:09.678
We're a team, okay?

48:11.346 --> 48:12.806
Till death do us part.

48:12.890 --> 48:16.393
[Joe] Clearly, my plan has backfired.
My wife seems more into me than ever.

48:32.326 --> 48:36.788
Swinging was supposed to be
my marriage's dying gasp, not theirs.

48:39.207 --> 48:43.086
How the fuck are these two
getting out of here alive?

48:47.090 --> 48:48.800
[theme music playing]
